track tads
superTrack on hide
shortLabel TADs
longLabel Topologically associating domains (TADs) from Hi-C studies
group regulation
html tads

track tadsDixon
parent tads
priority 1
compositeTrack on
shortLabel Dixon 2012 TADs
longLabel TAD domains in mESC and cortex (Dixon et al. 2012, lifted from mm9)
type bigBed 4
group regulation
visibility pack
html tadsDixon

    track tadsDixonMESC
    parent tadsDixon on
    shortLabel mESC TADs
    longLabel TAD domains in mouse embryonic stem cells (Dixon et al. 2012, lifted from mm9)
    type bigBed 4
    bigDataUrl /gbdb/$D/bbi/tad/tadsDixonMESC.bb
    color 27,158,119
    mouseOver <b>Cell type:</b> $name (TAD domain)

    track tadsDixonCortex
    parent tadsDixon on
    shortLabel Cortex TADs
    longLabel TAD domains in mouse cortex (Dixon et al. 2012, lifted from mm9)
    type bigBed 4
    bigDataUrl /gbdb/$D/bbi/tad/tadsDixonCortex.bb
    color 106,61,154
    mouseOver <b>Cell type:</b> $name (TAD domain)

include tadsEncode.ra

include tads3dgb.ra
